Easy A -LRB- stylized as easy A -RRB- is a 2010 American teen comedy film directed by Will Gluck , written by Bert V. Royal and starring Emma Stone , Stanley Tucci , Patricia Clarkson , Thomas Haden Church , Dan Byrd , Amanda Bynes , Penn Badgley , Cam Gigandet , Lisa Kudrow and Aly Michalka .
The screenplay was partially inspired by the novel The Scarlet Letter by Nathaniel Hawthorne .
Shot at Screen Gems studios and in Ojai , California , the film was released on September 17 , 2010 , received positive reviews and grossed $ 75 million worldwide .